\begin_layout Plain Layout
antimagic clouds
\end_layout

\end_inset

, which prevent any spell casting or targeting inside them, and fade slowly.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Webs cover anyone entering with goo, which slows the victim down.
 Pausing
